<h1>Cannabis: An apology</h1>
	</em>
</p>
<p class="tagline"><!--proximic_content_on-->In 1997, this newspaper launched a campaign to decriminalise the drug. If only we had known then what we can reveal today...<!--proximic_content_off--></p>
